flowchart TD
    A[Security Event Detected] --> B{Event Severity}
    B -->|Critical| C[Immediate Alert - SOC]
    B -->|High| D[Priority Alert - Security Team]
    B -->|Medium/Low| E[Standard Alert - Operations]
    
    C --> F[Incident Commander Assigned]
    D --> G[Senior Security Analyst]
    E --> H[Security Analyst]
    
    F --> I[Immediate Containment]
    G --> J[Investigation & Analysis]
    H --> K[Standard Investigation]
    
    I --> L[Impact Assessment]
    J --> L
    K --> L
    
    L --> M{Business Impact?}
    M -->|High| N[Executive Notification]
    M -->|Medium| O[Management Notification]
    M -->|Low| P[Team Notification]
    
    N --> Q[Emergency Response Team]
    O --> R[Security Team Response]
    P --> S[Standard Response]
    
    Q --> T[Remediation Actions]
    R --> T
    S --> T
    
    T --> U[Post-Incident Review]
    U --> V[Lessons Learned]
    V --> W[Security Improvements]
    
    style A fill:#FFB6C1
    style C fill:#FF6B6B
    style I fill:#FFA500
    style T fill:#90EE90